item.dc:creator: @kickingjamie kickingjamie
item.description:
@kickingjamie wrote:

I don’t understand what you need, is your problem you can’t make the buttons work?

If your trying to make the buttons work by using the custom command method I can help with that.

This code will connect the original yes button to your command “home”.

case 168: //the button id. if (teleblock == true) { sendMessage("A magical force stops you from teleporting."); } else { customCommand("home"); // the command name in your cutomCommand method. } break;
